channel.title: Amped Up 317 Client
channel.description:
Currently constructing Amped Up Client V1. I will be making 2 versions of it and releasing them at the same time. A CoD: Modern Warfare 2 version and a regular version. I will keep posting pics of it, this is just an announcement.
***UPDATE*** First pic of Modern Warfare 2 Client-- [IMG]http://i296.photobucket.com/albums/mm187/RyanR0x/evolved0008-2.png[/img]
I'm still editing so throw some ideas at me and i will see what i can do with them.
***2nd UPDATE*** First pic of Amped Up V1 [IMG]http://i296.photobucket.com/albums/mm187/RyanR0x/evolved0009-1.png[/img]
Looking good yet?
